<typeStatus id="54C334D9E803513F7B3BFE6A3ADDFE32" box="[1389,1436,446,469]" pageId="3" pageNumber="38">type</typeStatus>
locality, Cúc PhƯƠng National Park. The species name is a noun in apposition.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
